com.stormpath.sdk.mail

Interface UnmodeledEmailTemplate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EmailTemplate<UnmodeledEmailTemplate>, Resource, Saveable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultUnmodeledEmailTemplate

    public interface UnmodeledEmailTemplate
extends EmailTemplate<UnmodeledEmailTemplate>
    The UnmodeledEmailTemplate is an EmailTemplate resource that will be sent to the user after the newly-created account has been successfully verified. For example, this email can be used to notify the user about his admittance to start using your service as a fully registered user.
    Since:
    1.0.RC4.5
